channel.title: !Obsidian Radio Official MC SERVER!
channel.description:
This is the official minecraft server for the upcoming online radio station Obsidian Radio. Our goal is to provide everyone with a radio station the they the enjoy and to run a server for listeners to have fun on. everyone is welcome to join and play on this server. For more information check out our planet minecraft page.
